<h1>What can MAC offer?</h1>
<ul>
<li>
<h2>Strong separation of security domains</h2>
<ul>
<li>Separate data based on confidentiality/integrity/purpose</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<h2>System, application, and data integrity</h2>
<ul>
<li>Protect against unauthorized modifications</li>
<li>Prevent ill-formed modifications</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<h2>Ability to limit program privileges</h2>
<ul>
<li>Safely run code of uncertain trustworthiness</li>
<li>Prevent exploit of flaw in program from escalating
privilege</li>
<li>Limit each program to only what is required for its
purpose</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
